learning about npm scripts and why should we use them

npm scipts:

these are the script which we use in our project to do some special things like :
starting our project
running tests 
linting code
etc.


these  provide commands that are liek placeholders for some other commands 

 they have special keywords for difeerent  types of scripts 

 they are very usefyull as they help the user perform important actions based on the file prefernce 